<body>
<pb type="new" n="416" facs="#p350"/>
<pb type="original" n="350" />
<head>
<persName ref="#SarahSands">Sarah Sands</persName> seall <graphic url=""/> Block island alias new shorum
</head>



<div type="entry" n="will">
    <div type="section" n="header">
        <ab>
            <lb/>In
            <w xml:id="the"><choice><abbr>þ<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>the</expan></choice></w>
            name of God Amen I <persName ref="#SarahSands">Sarah Sands</persName> of
            <lb/><placeName>Block island alias new shorum in <w copyOf="#the"/> Coliny of Rhod is
            <lb break="no"/>Land and providence plantations in new ingland</placeName>
            <lb/>being aged and weake in body but of sound and
            <lb/>perfect memory praise be given to allmighty
            <lb/>God for <w copyOf="#the"/> same and knowing <w copyOf="#the"/> unsertainty of this
            <lb/>Life one Earth and being desireous to settel things
            <lb/>in order Before my death dow make this my last
            <lb/>will and testament in maner and forme foloing
        </ab>
    </div>
    <div type="section" n="overview">
        <div type="clause" n="dower">
            <ab>
                <lb/>I being wife to
                <persName ref="#JamesSandsSr">
                <roleName type="honorific" full="abb">
                <choice><abbr>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>Mister</expan></choice>
                </roleName>
                James Sands
                </persName>
                deseased and
                <lb/>made sole executrix by my
                <w xml:id="said"><choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan>said</expan></choice></w>
                husband as by will
                <lb/>bareing date
                <date calendar="julian" datingMethod="julian" when-custom="1694-06-18">
                    June <w copyOf="#the"/> 18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1694
                </date>
                may plainly appear
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div type="clause" n="soul">
            <ab>
                <lb/>that is to saye first and prinsipally I commend my
                <lb/>soul to allmity God my creatur assueredly be<pc force="weak">-</pc>
                <lb break="no"/>leiving that I shall receive full pardon and free
                <lb/>remision of all my sins and be savid by <w copyOf="#the"/> presi
                <lb break="no"/>ous death and merits of my blesed saviour and re
                <lb break="no"/>deamer Christ Jesus
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div type="clause" n="body">
            <ab>
                and my body to <w copyOf="#the"/> earth from
                <lb/>whence it was first tacken to be buried in such dease
                <seg type="turnover"><lb/><pc force="weak">(</pc>nt</seg>
                <lb/>and Christian maner as to my <rs type="person" ref="#EdwardSands">executer</rs> hearafter
                <lb/>named shall be thought most meet and convenient
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div type="clause" n="estate">
            <ab>
                <lb/>and as touching such worldly <seg xml:id="estate">estate</seg> as <w copyOf="#the"/> Lord in
                <lb/>marcy hath lent me my will and meaning is <seg corresp="#estate"><w copyOf="#the"/>
                <lb/>same</seg> shall be impleied and bestowed as hear
                <lb break="no"/>after by this my will is exspresed
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div type="clause" n="revoke">
            <ab>
                and first I dow
                <lb/>renounce revock <choice><orig>floustarate</orig><reg>frustrate</reg></choice> and make void all
                <lb/>wills by me formerly made and declared and apoint
                <lb/>this my last will and testament in maner and form
                <lb/>following
            </ab>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div type="section" n="items">
        <div n="1" type="item">
            <ab>
                Itum furst I give and bequea<subst><del>f</del><add type="overwrite">th</add></subst> and
                <lb/>my will is that all my debts and funarall charg
                <seg type="turnover"><lb/><pc force="weak">(</pc>es</seg>
                <lb/>be payed and discharged
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div n="2" type="item">
            <ab>
                Item 2ly I give and
                <lb/>prins<subst><del rend="overstrike">e</del><add type="overwrite">a</add></subst>pelly
                make my youngest sonn <persName ref="#EdwardSands">Edward Sands</persName>
                <lb/>my sole executor of all my hole estate both catell sheep
                <lb/>hors coyne and housal stuf or what so ever I shall leave
                <lb/>at my death exsepting and reserving what is hear
                <lb break="no"/>after mentioned which is five cows and one hun
                <lb break="no"/>dred sheep which my will is that thay shall be e
                <lb break="no"/>quilly devided amoungst my five children which
                <lb/>are as followeth
                    <persName ref="#JohnSands">John Sands</persName>
                    <persName ref="#JamesSandsJr">James Sands</persName>
                    <persName ref="#SamuelSands">Samuel<lb/>Sands</persName> and
                    <persName ref="#SarahNiles">Sarah Niels</persName> and
                    <persName ref="#MercyRaymond">Marcy Ramond</persName> and
                <lb/>dow freely give and bequea<unclear>f</unclear>e to each of them
                <pb type="new" n="417" facs="#p351"/>
                <pb type="original" n="351" />
                <fw type="pageNum" place="top" rend="center circled">351</fw>
                <lb/>all former gifts or monys due to me from them all
                <lb break="no"/>ways

                provided that <persName ref="#JamesSandsJr">James Sands</persName> doth forever aqui<unclear>r</unclear>
                <seg type="turnover"><lb/><unclear>e</unclear></seg>
                <lb/>any protended <del rend="overstrike"><unclear>or</unclear></del> right or clame of asertain<pc>:</pc> ne
                <lb break="no"/>gero woman comanly caled by <w copyOf="#the"/> name of <persName ref="#Leano">Leano</persName> <pc>- -</pc>
                <lb/>bought of <persName ref="#DavidBrown">David Broun</persName>
                otherways <w copyOf="#the"/> <w copyOf="#said"/> <persName ref="#JamesSandsJr">James
                <lb/>Sands</persName> shall paye to <w copyOf="#the"/> person home shall be dispose
                <seg type="turnover"><lb/><pc force="weak">(</pc>s</seg>
                <lb break="no"/>ed of <w copyOf="#said"/> <rs type="person" ref="#Leano">neagore woman</rs> by <w copyOf="#said"/> <persName ref="#JamesSandsJr">Sands</persName> meanes
                <lb/>twenty pounds currant mony which he <w copyOf="#the"/> <w copyOf="#said"/> <persName ref="#JamesSandsJr">James
                <lb/>Sands</persName> hath allredy reseived of me tenn pounds by
                <lb/>his brother <persName ref="#JohnSands">John Sands</persName> and tenn pounds of <rs type="person" ref="#SarahSands">myself</rs>
                <lb/>in wool and cheas and butter which <rs type="person" ref="#JamesSandsJr">he</rs> hath received
                <lb/>upon <w copyOf="#the"/> acounte of <w copyOf="#said"/> <rs type="person" ref="#Leano">negero</rs>
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div n="3" type="item">
            <ab>
                Itum 3 I give to
                <lb/>my grandaughter <persName ref="#SarahNiles2">Sarah Niels</persName> one good fether beed
                <lb/>and bolster and tow pillows and one blancket
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div n="4" type="item">
            <ab>
                Itum
                <lb/>4 I give to my daughter <persName ref="#MercyRaymond">Marcy Ramond</persName> one good
                <lb/>larg chest onely what goods shall be left in <w copyOf="#said"/> chest
                <lb/>shall be equilly devided betwene hurself and my
                <lb/>daughter in law <persName ref="#MarySands">Mary Sands</persName> wife to my sonn
                <lb/><persName ref="#EdwardSands">Edward Sands</persName>
            </ab>
        </div>
        <div n="5" type="item">
            <ab>
                Itum 5 I give to my tow daughters
                <lb/><persName ref="#SarahNiles">Sarah Niels</persName> and <persName ref="#MercyRaymond">Marcy Ramond</persName> each of them a
                <lb/>good larg puter platter apease
            </ab>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div type="section" n="residue">
        <ab>
            all <w copyOf="#the"/> rest of my <w copyOf="#said"/>
            <lb/><seg corresp="#estate">estate</seg> I dow freely give unto my executor <persName ref="#EdwardSands">Ed
            <lb break="no"/>ward Sands</persName> him and his hayors forever
        </ab>
    </div>
    <div type="section" n="execution">
        <ab>
            as<pc> - -</pc>
            <lb/>witness my hand and seall this
            <date calendar="julian" datingMethod="julian" when-custom="1703-10-17">
                sevent<subst><del>h</del><add type="overwrite">eenth</add></subst>
                <lb/>of October one thousand seven hundred and<lb/>three
            </date>
            and
            <date datingMethod="EnglandRegnalYear" when-custom="2 Anne">
                in <w copyOf="#the"/> second year of hur magistys
                <lb/>Queen An of Ingland Scotland
            </date>
            <pc>¶</pc>
            <lb/>
            <lb/><persName ref="#SarahSands">Sarah Sands</persName> hur seall <graphic url=""/>
        </ab>
    </div>
    <div type="section" n="witness">
        <p>
            <lb/>signed sealed and delivered in presence of<lb/>us
            <lb/><persName ref="#SamuelNiles">Samuel Niels</persName>
            <lb/><persName ref="#HannahRose">Hanah Rose</persName> hur mark H
            <lb/><persName ref="#NathanielMott">Nathell Mot</persName>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<div type="entry" n="certified">
    <p>
        <lb/>A tru copy taken
        <lb/>out of <w copyOf="#the"/> origanall
        <lb/>will by me <persName ref="#JobCard">Job
        <lb/>Card <roleName type="office">Town
        <lb/>Clark</roleName></persName>
    </p>
</div>
<div type="entry" n="proved">
    <p>
        <lb/>At a meeting at <w copyOf="#the"/> hous of <persName ref="#EdwardBall">Edward Ball</persName>s
        <lb/>by <w copyOf="#the"/> Town Counsell of Shorum
        <date calendar="julian" datingMethod="julian" when-custom="1709-06-13">
            June <w copyOf="#the"/> 13<hi rend="sup">th</hi><lb/>1709
        </date>
        <persName ref="#SamuelNiles">Samuel Niels</persName> of Kingstown and
        <lb/><persName ref="#NathanielMott">Nathanal Mott</persName> of Shorum both of <w copyOf="#the"/> Coliny
        <lb/>of Rhod Island personaly apearing before
        <lb/>us and testifeeing upon oath that <w copyOf="#the"/> <rs type="person" ref="#SarahSands">tes
        <lb break="no"/>tater</rs> was in her per<subst><del><gap reason="overwriting illegible" quantity="1" unit="chars"/></del><add type="overwrite">p</add></subst>het mind and
        <lb/>memory at <w copyOf="#the"/> signings
        <lb/>and sealing of this tes
        <lb break="no"/>tament
    </p>
    <p>
        <lb/>as atested by us
        <lb/><persName ref="#SimonRay">Simon Ray <roleName type="office">Ward<unclear>en</unclear></roleName></persName>
        <lb/>and <persName ref="#EdwardBall">Edward Ball <roleName type="office">War<unclear>den</unclear></roleName></persName>
    </p>
    <p>
        <lb/><persName ref="#SimonRay">Simon Ray</persName>
        <lb/><persName ref="#JobCard">Job Card</persName>
        <lb/><persName ref="#ThomasRathbone">Thomas Rathbon</persName>
    </p>
</div>



</body>
